snippet.title: Warp League Basketball - Trailer
snippet.description:
The sport of the future is basketball with guns.  Play 3-on-3 in VR!

Warp League is a hero shooter designed to be an accessible, competitive, and immersive VR experience! Choose a unique character, and use their special combat abilities to make big plays on the court!

Earn points by shooting hoops or by shooting enemies. Can your team score the most points in 10 minutes?

http://store.steampowered.com/app/536460/Warp_League_Basketball/
